{% comment %}
  About / Our Story — "SO WE DECIDED TO FIX IT" stamp card.
  The stamp background SVG is set inline (asset_url is unavailable inside
  {% stylesheet %}); all other styling is in the scoped stylesheet.
{% endcomment %}

<section class="about-fix about-fix-{{ section.id }} color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <div class="about-fix__container">

    <div class="about-fix__header">
      <div class="about-fix__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="{{ 'about-rose.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="100" height="100" loading="lazy">
      </div>

      <h2 class="about-fix__heading">SO WE DECIDED TO FIX IT</h2>

      <div class="about-fix__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="{{ 'about-rose.png' | asset_url }}" alt="" width="100" height="100" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-fix__box-wrapper">
      <div
        class="about-fix__bg-layer"
        style="background-image: url('{{ 'about-stamp-1.svg' | asset_url }}');"
      ></div>

      <div class="about-fix__content-layer">
        <div class="about-fix__text-inner">
          <p>We researched, tested, rejected, re-tested, and built a sourcing model that could preserve quality from soil to spoon.</p>
          <p><strong>We didn&rsquo;t want nostalgia. We wanted function.</strong></p>
          <p>So we studied each ingredient for what it actually does, what makes it effective, and how people can use it in a way that genuinely supports their health: without drama or fear.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .about-fix {
    background-color: #fbf3cc;
    padding: 20px 20px 40px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-fix__container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-fix__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-fix__heading {
    color: #f84b21;
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family, "Copperplate BFC", Georgia, serif);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 29px);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .about-fix__icon img {
    width: 60px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-fix__box-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    aspect-ratio: 760 / 300;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .about-fix__bg-layer {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    filter: drop-shadow(20px 20px 0 #ffc62f);
  }

  .about-fix__content-layer {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: #fbf3cc;
  }

  .about-fix__text-inner {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family, "Aesthet Nova", Georgia, serif);
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-fix__text-inner p {
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 0 80px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-fix__text-inner p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-fix__text-inner strong {
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-fix {
      padding: 12px 12px 0;
    }

    .about-fix__header {
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .about-fix__heading {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .about-fix__box-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .about-fix__bg-layer {
      display: none;
    }

    .about-fix__content-layer {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      color: #5d57c5;
    }

    .about-fix__text-inner {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .about-fix__text-inner p {
      padding: 0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-fix__text-inner strong {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Fix Stamp",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "color_scheme",
      "id": "color_scheme",
      "label": "Color scheme",
      "default": "scheme-1"
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "About Fix Stamp" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
